  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Disclaimer: This game contains prolonged sequences featuring strobe lighting and / or flashing effects.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NOW INCLUDES DIRECTOR'S CUT! Play the game with fixed cameras and tank controls for the classic survival horror experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a research centre on a recently discovered planet goes dark, an investigation is launched - which uncovers tragedy and leads to the mysterious destruction of the entire site. Now, 15 years later, a lone prospector heads to the former site in search of salvageable artefacts, only to unwittingly unleash a dangerous mutagenic anomaly onboard a nearby service station. Trapped and alone, he is forced to fight for his life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494730/extras/bc615d03dccb11bd6cd8221961faddb5.poster.avif?t=1750095617\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494730/extras/bc615d03dccb11bd6cd8221961faddb5.webm?t=1750095617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494730/extras/bc615d03dccb11bd6cd8221961faddb5.mp4?t=1750095617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival Horror<br>The absorbing, cerebral nature of traditional survival horror with limited inventory system and self-directed, non-linear progression, paired with a 3rd person, 360 degree player-controlled camera. The Prospector Odyssey is the perfect marriage of classic and modern design sensibilities. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494730/extras/8f59eb48affbed812c6d03ff6a2f733f.poster.avif?t=1750095617\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494730/extras/8f59eb48affbed812c6d03ff6a2f733f.webm?t=1750095617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494730/extras/8f59eb48affbed812c6d03ff6a2f733f.mp4?t=1750095617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think or Die<br>Solve intricate puzzles, find your own way around the dark, oppressive environments, be smart in your decisions of inventory management. Think carefully before heading into danger - there is no one coming to help...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494730/extras/fabb5e2812710b6b945408db1c26a58f.poster.avif?t=1750095617\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494730/extras/fabb5e2812710b6b945408db1c26a58f.webm?t=1750095617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494730/extras/fabb5e2812710b6b945408db1c26a58f.mp4?t=1750095617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight or Hide<br>Sneak your way past the lurking dangers undetected or do your best to stand up to the relentless terrors. Craft defensive items with scarce resources. Search thoroughly for weapons and supplies to aid your survival. </p></li></ul>",
