loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494730/extras/8f59eb48affbed812c6d03ff6a2f733f.poster.avif?t=1750095617\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494730/extras/8f59eb48affbed812c6d03ff6a2f733f.webm?t=1750095617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494730/extras/8f59eb48affbed812c6d03ff6a2f733f.mp4?t=1750095617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think or Die<br>Solve intricate puzzles, find your own way around the dark, oppressive environments, be smart in your decisions of inventory management. Think carefully before heading into danger - there is no one coming to help...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494730/extras/fabb5e2812710b6b945408db1c26a58f.poster.avif?t=1750095617\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494730/extras/fabb5e2812710b6b945408db1c26a58f.webm?t=1750095617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494730/extras/fabb5e2812710b6b945408db1c26a58f.mp4?t=1750095617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight or Hide<br>Sneak your way past the lurking dangers undetected or do your best to stand up to the relentless terrors. Craft defensive items with scarce resources. Search thoroughly for weapons and supplies to aid your survival. </p></li></ul>",
